            <title>[HBASE-2891] Allow rowcounter to process multiple tables in one run</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2891</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently rowcounter accepts one table for each run.&lt;br/&gt;
It is desirable to add capability to process multiple tables in one run.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
